fields.title: about
fields.content:
Since its creation in 2008, jar spreads its positive energy & sweet tales @ Syros island. George and Martin are waiting to delight you with their exquisite, on-the spot prepared pastries[forest fruit & strawberry cheese-cake, lemon merinque pie, quiche, pies and others] beverages and funky cocktails for your soul! From 09:00 till 03:00 a.m. non-stop smooth trip. New recipes coming-up all the time with lots of imagination and creativity in Martin's saucers and George's shaker! Summer starts at 7th of June!


The best coffee & sweet tales place @ Syros island. George and Martin are waiting to delight you with their exquisite, on-the spot prepared pastries [forest fruit & strawberry cheese-cake, lemonpie, mille-feuille, quiche Lorraine and others) coffee and coctails.

From 08:00 till 03:00 a.m. non-stop.
New recipees coming-up all the time with lots of imagination and creativity in Martin's saucers!!!
